'''2013年7月貝魯特爆炸案'''是指在2013年7月9日時於[[貝魯特|貝魯特]]南郊比爾埃爾-阿貝德（Bir el-Abed）的汽車炸彈爆炸，造成至少53人受傷。其中比爾埃爾-阿貝德被認為是[[真主黨|真主黨]]的據點，對此真主黨和[[萨阿德·哈里里|萨阿德·哈里里]]將爆炸案歸咎於「以色列和它的代理人」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.courrierinternational.com/breve/2013/07/10/attentat-a-beyrouth-dans-le-fief-du-hezbollah |title=LIBAN • Attentat à Beyrouth dans le fief du Hezbollah {{!}} Courrier international<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-02-14 |archive-date=2018-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021065928/https://www.courrierinternational.com/breve/2013/07/10/attentat-a-beyrouth-dans-le-fief-du-hezbollah |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但其他觀察家懷疑這講法是為了保持遜尼派和什葉派的和平，並且安撫當時因為真主黨支持敘利亞總統[[巴沙爾·阿薩德|巴沙爾·阿薩德]]而強烈不滿的遜尼派人士<ref name=barnard>{{cite news|last=BARNARD|first=ANNE|title=Car Bombing Injures Dozens in Hezbollah Section of Beirut|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/10/world/middleeast/syria.html?_r=0|accessdate=30 August 2013|newspaper=New York Times|date=9 July 2013|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111235247/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/10/world/middleeast/syria.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://world.time.com/2013/07/09/car-bomb-hits-beiruts-southern-suburbs-on-first-day-of-ramadan/photo/civil-defence-members-security-personnel-and-civilians-gather-at-the-site-of-an-explosion-in-beiruts-southern-suburbs/ "Car Bomb Hits Beirut’s Southern Suburbs on First Day of Ramadan".] {{Wayback|url=http://world.time.com/2013/07/09/car-bomb-hits-beiruts-southern-suburbs-on-first-day-of-ramadan/photo/civil-defence-members-security-personnel-and-civilians-gather-at-the-site-of-an-explosion-in-beiruts-southern-suburbs/ |date=20171012115930 }} ''[[時代雜誌|Time]]''.</ref><ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2013/jul/09/bomb-explodes-in-beirut-video "Car bomb explodes in Hezbollah neighbourhood of Beirut".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2013/jul/09/bomb-explodes-in-beirut-video |date=20181020224128 }} ''[[衛報|The Guardian]]''.</ref>。

